---
title: Lemon Drizzle Cake & Almond Crunch with Passionfruit Lemon Sauce | Serves 6+
description: Zingy, bright and oh-so tasty! Lemon drizzle cake gets its name from a sweet lemony syrup that's poured over the cake while it's still warm to ensure it stays moist, tender and totally infused with zesty citrus flavours.
